race.comment: SYDNEY DANGER (6) was game in defeat at the latest run, finishing third and beaten 0.6 lengths (19.72) behind Handle Bars Down at Hobart. The form out of the last run is proven to be strong. Winning claims. DISFUNCTIONAL (1) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (20.39) last time in a Restricted WIN at Hobart. One of the better chances. HELLYER DOUGIE (2) showed good early burn and was there until turning but swamped late to finish 7th at this track in a Grade 3/4. Key player if finds best. WYNBURN SWEETIE (3) with some luck can improve on an unplaced run last time here.
